#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:1
msgid "Helpdesk (`lu_mcp_helpdesk`)"
msgstr "Helpdesk (`lu_mcp_helpdesk`)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:3
msgid "**12 tools** for the full Odoo Helpdesk ticket lifecycle."
msgstr "Odoo 헬프데스크 티켓 라이프사이클 전체를 위한 **12가지 도구**입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:5
msgid "Requires: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `helpdesk` app."
msgstr "필요 조건: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `helpdesk` 앱."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:9
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "개요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:11
msgid ""
"These tools cover everything from ticket creation to closure: list teams "
"and stages, search and read tickets, create and update tickets, reply "
"(public or internal), escalate, close, check SLA status, view customer "
"history, and link Knowledge articles."
msgstr "이 도구들은 티켓 생성부터 종료까지의 모든 과정을 다룹니다: 팀과 스테이지 나열, 티켓 검색 및 읽기, 티켓 생성 및 업데이트, 답글 작성(공개 또는 내부), 에스컬레이션, 종료, SLA 상태 확인, 고객 이력 보기, Knowledge 아티클 연결."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:15
msgid ""
"**Priority values**: `'0'` = Low, `'1'` = Medium, `'2'` = High, `'3'` = "
"Urgent."
msgstr "**우선순위 값**: `'0'` = Low, `'1'` = Medium, `'2'` = High, `'3'` = Urgent."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:19
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "도구"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:21
msgid "`helpdesk_list_teams`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_list_teams`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:23
msgid ""
"List all helpdesk teams with open/unassigned/urgent ticket counts and SLA"
" success rate."
msgstr "모든 헬프데스크 팀의 열린/미할당/긴급 티켓 수 및 SLA 성공률을 나열합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "파라미터"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Type"
msgstr "유형"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Required"
msgstr "필수"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Description"
msgstr "설명"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "*(none)*"
msgstr "*(없음)*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:29 ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:42
#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:63 ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:77
#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:98 ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:119
#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:152 ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:168
#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:184 ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:199
#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:215
msgid "**Example prompt**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:30
msgid "*\"Show all helpdesk teams and how many open tickets each has.\"*"
msgstr "*\"모든 헬프데스크 팀과 각 팀이 보유한 열린 티켓 수를 표시하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:34
msgid "`helpdesk_list_stages`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_list_stages`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:36
msgid "List helpdesk ticket stages, optionally filtered to a team."
msgstr "헬프데스크 티켓 스테이지를 나열하며, 팀별로 필터링할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`team_id`"
msgstr "`team_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "integer"
msgstr "integer"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "No"
msgstr "아니요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Filter stages to a specific team. Omit for all stages."
msgstr "특정 팀의 스테이지만 필터링합니다. 전체 스테이지를 보려면 생략하세요."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:43
msgid "*\"What stages does the Support team (id=2) use?\"*"
msgstr "*\"Support 팀(id=2)은 어떤 스테이지를 사용하나요?\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:47
msgid "`helpdesk_search_tickets`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_search_tickets`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:49
msgid "Search tickets with multiple filters."
msgstr "여러 필터를 사용하여 티켓을 검색합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`query`"
msgstr "`query`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "string"
msgstr "string"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Keyword search in ticket name or description."
msgstr "티켓 이름 또는 설명에서 검색할 키워드."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Filter by team."
msgstr "팀별 필터링."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`stage_id`"
msgstr "`stage_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Filter by stage."
msgstr "스테이지별 필터링."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`assignee_id`"
msgstr "`assignee_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Filter by assignee (user ID)."
msgstr "담당자별 필터링(사용자 ID)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`partner_id`"
msgstr "`partner_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Filter by customer partner."
msgstr "고객 파트너별 필터링."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`priority`"
msgstr "`priority`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`'0'` Low, `'1'` Medium, `'2'` High, `'3'` Urgent."
msgstr "`'0'` Low, `'1'` Medium, `'2'` High, `'3'` Urgent."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`sla_failed`"
msgstr "`sla_failed`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "boolean"
msgstr "boolean"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "If `true`, return only SLA-failed tickets."
msgstr "값이 `true`이면 SLA 실패 티켓만 반환합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`include_closed`"
msgstr "`include_closed`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "If `true`, include tickets in closed (folded) stages. Default `false`."
msgstr "값이 `true`이면 폐쇄(폴드된) 스테이지의 티켓을 포함합니다. 기본값은 `false`입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`limit`"
msgstr "`limit`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Maximum results (default 20, max 80)."
msgstr "최대 결과 수(기본값 20, 최대 80)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:64
msgid ""
"*\"Show me all urgent tickets in the Support team that have failed their "
"SLA.\"*"
msgstr "*\"Support 팀의 모든 긴급 티켓 중 SLA를 놓친 것들을 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:68
msgid "`helpdesk_read_ticket`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_read_ticket`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:70
msgid ""
"Get full details of a ticket: team, stage, priority, assignee, customer, "
"SLA status, timing metrics, and description."
msgstr "티켓의 전체 상세 정보(팀, 스테이지, 우선순위, 담당자, 고객, SLA 상태, 시간 측정값, 설명)를 가져옵니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`ticket_id`"
msgstr "`ticket_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "예"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Ticket ID."
msgstr "티켓 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:78
msgid "*\"Show me all details for ticket #305.\"*"
msgstr "*\"티켓 #305의 모든 상세 정보를 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:82
msgid "`helpdesk_create_ticket`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_create_ticket`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:84
msgid "Create a new helpdesk ticket."
msgstr "새 헬프데스크 티켓을 생성합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`name`"
msgstr "`name`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Ticket subject."
msgstr "티켓 제목."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Team to assign the ticket to."
msgstr "티켓을 할당할 팀."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`description`"
msgstr "`description`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Ticket description (Markdown)."
msgstr "티켓 설명(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Customer partner ID (links to existing contact)."
msgstr "고객 파트너 ID(기존 연락처에 연결)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`partner_email`"
msgstr "`partner_email`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Customer email (used if `partner_id` not provided)."
msgstr "고객 이메일(`partner_id`를 제공하지 않은 경우 사용)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`partner_name`"
msgstr "`partner_name`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Customer name (used if `partner_id` not provided)."
msgstr "고객 이름(`partner_id`를 제공하지 않은 경우 사용)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`'0'`–`'3'` (default `'0'` Low)."
msgstr "`'0'`~`'3'`(기본값 `'0'` Low)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "User ID of the agent to assign."
msgstr "할당할 담당자의 사용자 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`tag_ids`"
msgstr "`tag_ids`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "array of integer"
msgstr "array of integer"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Tag IDs to apply."
msgstr "적용할 태그 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:99
msgid ""
"*\"Create a high-priority helpdesk ticket titled 'Login broken for user "
"jsmith@acme.com' in the IT Support team.\"*"
msgstr "*\"IT Support 팀에서 'Login broken for user jsmith@acme.com'이라는 제목의 높은 우선순위 헬프데스크 티켓을 생성하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:103
msgid "`helpdesk_update_ticket`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_update_ticket`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:105
msgid "Update an existing ticket's fields."
msgstr "기존 티켓의 필드를 업데이트합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Ticket ID to update."
msgstr "업데이트할 티켓 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "New subject."
msgstr "새 제목."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "New description (Markdown)."
msgstr "새 설명(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Move to a different stage."
msgstr "다른 스테이지로 이동."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Move to a different team."
msgstr "다른 팀으로 이동."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Reassign to a different agent."
msgstr "다른 담당자에게 재할당."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "New priority (`'0'`–`'3'`)."
msgstr "새 우선순위(`'0'`~`'3'`)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Replace tag set (pass empty array to clear)."
msgstr "태그 세트 교체(비우려면 빈 배열 전달)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`kanban_state`"
msgstr "`kanban_state`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`normal`, `done`, or `blocked`."
msgstr "`normal`, `done`, `blocked` 중 하나."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:120
msgid "*\"Reassign ticket #305 to user #7 and set priority to Urgent.\"*"
msgstr "*\"티켓 #305를 사용자 #7에게 재할당하고 우선순위를 Urgent로 설정하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:124
msgid "`helpdesk_ticket_reply`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_ticket_reply`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:126
msgid "Post a reply or internal note on a ticket."
msgstr "티켓에 답글 또는 내부 메모를 작성합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`body`"
msgstr "`body`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Reply body (Markdown)."
msgstr "답글 본문(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`internal`"
msgstr "`internal`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid ""
"If `true`, post as internal note (not visible to customer). Default "
"`false`."
msgstr "값이 `true`이면 내부 메모로 작성됩니다(고객에게 보이지 않음). 기본값은 `false`입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:134
msgid "**Example prompt — customer reply**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트 — 고객 답글**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:135
msgid ""
"*\"Reply to ticket #305: 'We have identified the issue and will deploy a "
"fix by EOD tomorrow.'\"*"
msgstr "*\"티켓 #305에 답글: 'We have identified the issue and will deploy a fix by EOD tomorrow.'\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:137
msgid "**Example prompt — internal note**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트 — 내부 메모**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:138
msgid ""
"*\"Add an internal note to ticket #305: 'Root cause was a misconfigured "
"nginx rule on server A.'\"*"
msgstr "*\"티켓 #305에 내부 메모 추가: 'Root cause was a misconfigured nginx rule on server A.'\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:142
msgid "`helpdesk_ticket_close`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_ticket_close`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:144
msgid ""
"Close a ticket by moving it to the first closed (folded) stage. "
"Optionally posts a resolution message."
msgstr "첫 번째 폐쇄(폴드된) 스테이지로 이동하여 티켓을 종료합니다. 선택적으로 해결 메시지를 작성할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Resolution summary to post as a customer message (Markdown)."
msgstr "고객 메시지로 작성할 해결 요약(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:153
msgid ""
"*\"Close ticket #305 with the message: 'Issue resolved. The fix has been "
"deployed.'\"*"
msgstr "*\"티켓 #305를 메시지와 함께 종료: 'Issue resolved. The fix has been deployed.'\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:157
msgid "`helpdesk_ticket_escalate`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_ticket_escalate`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:159
msgid "Raise the priority of a ticket by one level and optionally reassign it."
msgstr "티켓의 우선순위를 한 단계 올리고 선택적으로 재할당합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid ""
"Target priority (`'0'`–`'3'`). If omitted, increments by one (max `'3'` "
"Urgent)."
msgstr "대상 우선순위(`'0'`~`'3'`). 생략하면 1씩 증가합니다(최대 `'3'` Urgent)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Move to escalation team."
msgstr "에스컬레이션 팀으로 이동."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Assign to escalation agent."
msgstr "에스컬레이션 담당자에게 할당."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:169
msgid ""
"*\"Escalate ticket #305 to the Tier 2 team (id=4) and assign to agent "
"#9.\"*"
msgstr "*\"티켓 #305를 Tier 2 팀(id=4)으로 에스컬레이션하고 담당자 #9에게 할당하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:173
msgid "`helpdesk_get_sla_status`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_get_sla_status`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:175
msgid ""
"Get SLA policies for a team, or detailed SLA compliance status for a "
"specific ticket."
msgstr "팀의 SLA 정책을 조회하거나 특정 티켓의 자세한 SLA 준수 상태를 가져옵니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "List SLA policies for this team."
msgstr "이 팀의 SLA 정책을 나열합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Get per-policy SLA status for a specific ticket."
msgstr "특정 티켓의 정책별 SLA 상태를 가져옵니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:182
msgid ""
"Pass either `team_id` (to see configured policies) or `ticket_id` (to see"
" compliance)."
msgstr "`team_id`(설정된 정책을 보기 위해) 또는 `ticket_id`(준수 상황을 보기 위해) 중 하나를 전달하세요."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:185
msgid "*\"What is the SLA status for ticket #305?\"*"
msgstr "*\"티켓 #305의 SLA 상태는 무엇입니까?\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:189
msgid "`helpdesk_customer_history`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_customer_history`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:191
msgid "Get ticket history and satisfaction ratings for a customer."
msgstr "고객의 티켓 이력 및 만족도 평가를 가져옵니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Customer partner ID. At least one of `partner_id` or `email` required."
msgstr "고객 파트너 ID. `partner_id` 또는 `email` 중 최소 하나는 필수입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`email`"
msgstr "`email`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Customer email address."
msgstr "고객 이메일 주소."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Maximum tickets to return (default 20, max 80)."
msgstr "반환할 최대 티켓 수(기본값 20, 최대 80)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:200
msgid "*\"Show the helpdesk history for customer john@acme.com.\"*"
msgstr "*\"고객 john@acme.com의 헬프데스크 이력을 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:204
msgid "`helpdesk_link_knowledge_article`"
msgstr "`helpdesk_link_knowledge_article`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:206
msgid ""
"Link a Knowledge article to a ticket by appending its URL to the ticket "
"description."
msgstr "티켓 설명에 URL을 추가하여 Knowledge 아티클을 티켓에 연결합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:208
msgid "Requires: Odoo `knowledge` app installed."
msgstr "필요 조건: Odoo `knowledge` 앱이 설치되어 있어야 합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Helpdesk ticket ID."
msgstr "헬프데스크 티켓 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "`article_id`"
msgstr "`article_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md
msgid "Knowledge article ID to link."
msgstr "연결할 Knowledge 아티클 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:216
msgid "*\"Link Knowledge article #77 (Troubleshooting Guide) to ticket #305.\"*"
msgstr "*\"Knowledge 아티클 #77(Troubleshooting Guide)을 티켓 #305에 연결하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/helpdesk.md:219
msgid "This tool is only registered when the `knowledge` Odoo app is installed."
msgstr "이 도구는 Odoo `knowledge` 앱이 설치된 경우에만 등록됩니다."
